8X8</ref>\n* Region 4: March 22, 2012<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B01ECL2MWQ</ref>\n|-\n| Super Babies' Dream Adventure\n| \n* Dora Helps the Birthday Wizzle\n* Pirate Treasure Hunt\n* Benny's Treasure\n| \n* Region 1: 19 July 2005<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B0009CTVKO</ref> & May 26, 2009<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B001TWT0C2</ref>\n* Region 4: _<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B01DJ61V18</ref>\n|-\n| Dora Saves the Crystal Kingdom\n| \n* First Day of School\n* Boots' Banana Wish\n| \n* Region 1: September 22, 2009 & March 6, 2012<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B006O51X6A</ref>\n* Region 4: July 1, 2010<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B077622274</ref>\n|-\n| colspan=\"2\"| Dora's Christmas Carol Adventure\n| \n* Region 1: November 3, 2009<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B002L9N4XS</ref>\n* Region 4: November 4, 2010<ref>https://www.jbhifi.com.au/products/dora-the-explorer-dora-christmas-carol-2009-dvd</ref>\n|-\n| Let's Explore!\n| \n* Lost Map\n* Hide and Go Seek\n* Journey to the Purple Planet\n* Rescue, Rescue, Rescue! \n* Star Catcher\n* Star Mountain\n* Boots to the Rescue\n* Swiper the Explorer \n| \n* Region 1: February 2, 2010<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B002VJ05DU</ref>\n|-\n| Explore the Earth\n| \n* Mixed-Up Seasons\n* To the South Pole\n* Save Diego\n* Beaches\n| \n* Region 1: April 13, 2010<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B003498SEE</ref>\n|-\n| Dora's Big Birthday Adventure\n| \n* Dora Helps the Birthday Wizzle\n* Wizzle Wishes \n| \n* Region 1: August 3, 2010<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B003KSO3PM</ref>\n* Region 4: September 09, 2010<ref>https://www.jbhifi.com.au/products/dora-the-explorer-doras-big-birthday-adventure-2010-dvd</ref>\n|-\n| Dora's Slumber Party\n| \n* Boots' Cuddly Dinosaur \n* Louder!\n* The Lost City\n* Little Star\n* Super Babies' Dream Adventure\n* Dora Had a Little Lamb\n| \n* Region 1: September 14, 2010<ref>https://www.amazon.com.au/dp/B003SLEDGA</ref>\n|-\n| It's Haircut Day!\n| \n* Dora's Hai