emala}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 129\n| [[UTC\u221206:00|UTC/GMT -6 hours]]\n|[[Central America]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{flagicon|Haiti}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Coat of arms of Haiti.svg|20px]]\n| [[Haiti]]\n|[[Port-au-Prince]]\n| Ha\u00efti; Ayiti\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 27,750\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| {{UN_Population|Haiti}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 350\n| [[UTC\u221204:00|UTC/GMT -4 hours]]\n|[[Caribbean]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{flagicon|HND}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Coat of arms of Honduras.svg|20px]]\n| [[Honduras]]\n|[[Tegucigalpa]]\n| Honduras\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 112,492\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| {{UN_Population|Honduras}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 76\n| [[UTC\u221206:00|UTC/GMT -6 hours]]\n|[[Central America]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{flagicon|Martinique|local}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:BlasonMartinique.svg|20px]]\n| [[Martinique]]*\n|[[Fort-de-France]]\n| Martinique\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1,128\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| {{UN_Population|Martinique}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 340\n| [[UTC\u221204:00|UTC/GMT -4 hours]]\n|[[Caribbean]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{flagicon|MEX}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Coat of arms of Mexico.svg|20px]]\n| [[Mexico]]\n|[[Mexico City]]\n| M\u00e9xico\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1,964 375\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| {{UN_Population|Mexico}}\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 57\n| [[UTC\u221205:00|UTC/GMT -5 hours]] (''Zona Sureste'')<br />[[UTC\u221206:00|UTC/GMT -6 hours]] (''Zona Centro'')<br />[[UTC\u221207:00|UTC/GMT -7 hours]] (''Zona Pac\u00edfico'')<br />[[UTC\u221208:00|UTC/GMT -8 hours]] (''Zona Noroeste'')\n|[[North America]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{flagicon|NIC}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| [[File:Coat of arms of Nicaragua.svg|20px]]\n| [[Nicaragua]]\n|[[Managua]]\n| Nicaragua\n| style=\"text-align:right